technology.title: Aaron Rodgers wasn't seeking 'revenge' against the Packers, who gave him a reality check instead - AP News
technology.description: Aaron Rodgers was solid but not spectacular in his first-ever game against the Green Bay Packers. The Pittsburgh Steelers quarterback passed for 219 yards and two touchdowns in a 35-25 loss to the team he won four MVPs and a Super Bowl with earlier in his car…
